Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.86,0:00:05.93,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Something is definitely weird here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.39,0:00:07.60,Main,Shalsha,0,0,0,,It is weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.93,0:00:09.73,Main,Falfa,0,0,0,,Very weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.06,0:00:12.35,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,I find it strange, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.68,0:00:16.98,Flashback,Halkara,0,0,0,,Master, it's my turn to cook \Nthe day after tomorrow,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.13,0:00:19.80,Flashback,Halkara,0,0,0,,but would you mind swapping \Nso I can do it today instead?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.80,0:00:22.27,Flashback,Azusa,0,0,0,,Sure, that's fine. Is something going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.72,0:00:25.60,Flashback,Halkara,0,0,0,,I have things to do in \Nthe town of Nascúte...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.35,0:00:36.75,Flashback,Halkara,0,0,0,,It's important to make a fresh start!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.66,0:00:40.83,Flashback,Falfa,0,0,0,,Bye, grasshopper!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.57,0:00:44.66,Flashback,Halkara,0,0,0,,Goodbyes should always \Nbe clean and complete...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.38,0:00:49.88,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,Do you think Halkara intends to move out?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.26,0:00:51.46,Main,Shalsha,0,0,0,,No doubt about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.68,0:00:53.30,Main,Falfa,0,0,0,,I don't want her to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.15,0:00:58.32,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,But if that's what Halkara's \Ndecided to do...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.63,0:01:02.49,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,I'm back!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.49,0:01:04.58,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,I'm so hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.41,0:01:07.18,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.99,0:01:10.94,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Halkara...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.25,0:01:13.01,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Thanks for everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.01,0:01:14.95,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,Please be well in your new location.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.68,0:01:17.25,Main,Shalsha,0,0,0,,We'll miss you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.61,0:01:23.20,Main,Falfa,0,0,0,,I don't want you to go, Halkara!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.15,0:01:27.36,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Falfa, don't cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.36,0:01:29.25,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,We must see her off with smiles.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.69,0:01:32.39,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,What in the world is this all about?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.39,0:01:34.55,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,Why all the talk of leaving?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.71,0:01:35.74,Narration - Top,SFX,0,0,0,,Blink, blink!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.90,0:01:37.52,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,What? You're not moving out?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.52,0:01:39.54,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,I have no intention of doing that!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.78,0:01:42.82,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,But you mentioned looking for \Na new place in Nascúte...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.82,0:01:46.00,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,Yes, one to build my new factory in!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.39,0:01:47.39,Main,All,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.64,0:01:51.20,Main,All,0,0,0,,What?!
